name: Slavutych
description: Slavutych metro station is a connect point between two different worlds. One entrance is on village-like suburbs side and second is on elite skyscrappers side. I've been in one of that high buildings and opposing side looked like dystopian slum. But also I've been down there in the "slum" for 7 years riding 15km on bicycle to my girlfriend's home. Shot on Kodak Portra 400 film using 1978 Canon AE-1 manual camera.
